data.description: You'll love this wonderful large rambler in the desirable gated community of Eagle Point at American Lake. This home has it all! Dramatic vaulted & high ceilings, spacious great room, excellent layout. Cozy gas fireplace. French doors open to oversized patio perfect for outdoor entertaining, plumbed for gas BBQ. 3 bedrms +office space. Big kitchen w/breakfast bar & plenty of storage. Private master suite w/5-piece bath, soaking tub, walk-in closet & convenient door to access back yard patio. Large 2-car garage. Beautiful community boasts park, private dock & boat launch, clubhouse, RV parking. Enjoy being surrounded by nature, lake views & watching eagles soar. Truly a hard to find gem! Easy access to I-5 & JBLM. Home Warranty included.
